          "groupByPersonaDimension": "media_diet",
          "summaryKind": "llm_bucket_summary",
          "instruction": "For each media-diet segment, summarize in 1-2 sentences what tipped subscribe vs decline — catalog fit, reading habits, price, and/or substitutes. Be faithful and concise; do not invent facts."
